POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/send-email-otp-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ratelimit-test@example.com"
}

### Second request immediately after (should fail with rate limit error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/send-email-otp-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ratelimit-test@example.com"
}


